      • exportFiles

        public void exportFiles(java.lang.String batchInstanceID)
                 throws javax.xml.bind.JAXBException,
                        DCMAApplicationException
        This method simply reads the batch.xml file in the sFolderToBeExported. It finds the names of multipage tiff and pdf files from the batch.xml. Then it moves these files to the export to folder.
        Parameters:
        batchInstanceID - String batch instance identifier for current executing batch.
        Throws:
        {@link - JAXBException}
        {@link - DCMAApplicationException}
        javax.xml.bind.JAXBException
